---
title: 'Produktside'
description: ''
order: 4
---
{%- extends 'base.njk' -%}

{%- from "macros/button.njk" import button -%}
{%- from "macros/microcard.njk" import microcard -%}

{%- block content -%}
  <main class="grid py-8 text-lg md:py-12 grid-cols-layout">
    <div class="relative col-default md:col-wide md:mx-0 grid sm:grid-cols-[6rem_auto] gap-x-8 items-start mb-12 sm:pr-20 md:pr-0">
      {{ '/src/_includes/svg/pictograms/utvidet-barnetrygd.svg' | svgContents('w-full h-auto max-w-20 sm:ml-1 top-2 text-green-800 absolute right-0 sm:relative') | safe }}

      <div class="sm:col-start-2 sm:row-start-1">
        <h1 class="min-w-0 pr-24 mt-0.5 text-3xl font-semibold leading-tight sm:pr-0 sm:text-5xl sm:leading-tight">Utvidet barnetrygd</h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-base opacity-80">
          <span class="tracking-wider uppercase">Pengestøtte</span>
          <span class="px-1"> — </span>
          <span>Oppdatert 22. desember 2022</span>
        </p>

      </div>

      {# Intro #}
      <div class="sm:col-start-2 grid md:grid-cols-[2fr_1fr] gap-x-16 items-start gap-4 mt-8">
        <div class="markdown">
          <p>Du kan få utvidet barnetrygd når du bor alene med barn under 18 år. Dette er barnetrygd for et barn mer enn du faktisk bor sammen med.</p>

          <p>Du kan også få småbarnstillegg. Dette er et tillegg til utvidet barnetrygd for enslige forsørgere som har barn mellom 0 og 3 år, og som også mottar full overgangsstønad.</p>

          <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold">Utvidet barnetrygd er aktuelt for deg som</h4>
          <div class="flex mt-1.5 flex-wrap gap-2">
              {{ microcard({
                text: 'Er helt eller delvis alene med barn',
                class: 'fine:hover:bg-orange-100 fine:hover:shadow-none',
                dot: 'bg-orange-300'
              }) }}
              {{ microcard({
                text: 'Er alene med barn fordi den andre forelderen er død',
                class: 'fine:hover:bg-orange-100 fine:hover:shadow-none',
                dot: 'bg-orange-300'
              }) }}
          </div>
        </div>


        {# Innholdsfortegnelse #}
        <div class="w-full max-w-3xl mt-6 md:sticky md:col-start-2 md:top-4 md:row-span-2 md:mx-0 md:max-w-none md:-mt-1.5 md:pl-6 md:border-l md:border-gray-200">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Innhold</h2>
          {%- set index = sections.slice(1) -%}
          <ul class="pt-1">
            {%- for item in index -%}
              <li class="py-1.5 text-lg"><a class="text-blue-500 underline decoration-blue-300 hover:text-blue-800 md:pl-0.5 hover:no-underline" href="#{{ item.title | slugify }}">{{ item.title }}</a></li>
            {%- endfor -%}
          </ul>

          <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-semibold">Nyttig å vite</h2>
          <ul class="pt-1">
            <li class="py-1.5 text-lg"><a class="text-blue-500 underline decoration-blue-300 hover:text-blue-800 md:pl-0.5 hover:no-underline" href="#">Klagerettigheter</a></li>
            <li class="py-1.5 text-lg"><a class="text-blue-500 underline decoration-blue-300 hover:text-blue-800 md:pl-0.5 hover:no-underline" href="#">Lov om barnetrygd</a></li>
            <li class="py-1.5 text-lg"><a class="text-blue-500 underline decoration-blue-300 hover:text-blue-800 md:pl-0.5 hover:no-underline" href="#">Pensjonsopptjening for omsorgsarbeid</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        {# Filter + Innhold #}
        <div class="grid w-full max-w-3xl gap-4 md:row-start-2 md:mx-0 md:max-w-none">

          {# Filter #}
          <div class="px-6 py-4 mt-8 rounded sm:px-8 sm:py-6 bg-blue-50 max-w-prose">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Hva er situasjonen din?</h2>
            <p>Velg situasjonen som passer for deg, så viser vi bare informasjon om den.</p>

            <button class="flex items-center justify-between w-full gap-3 px-4 py-2.5 mt-4 bg-white border-b-2 border-gray-400 md:max-w-max" type="button">
              <span>Tilpass innholdet</span>
              {{ '/src/_includes/svg/icons/chevron-down.svg' | svgContents('w-4 h-4') | safe }}
            </button>
          </div>

          {# Innhold #}
          {%- for section in sections -%}
            {%- if not loop.first -%}
            <div class="relative grid mt-10 max-w-prose" id="{{ section.title | slugify }}">

              <h2 class="flex items-baseline gap-2 sm:gap-4 text-2xl font-semibold sm:text-3xl sm:leading-snug {{ 'md:-mt-2' if section.icon }}">
                {%- if section.icon -%}
                <span class="inline-grid p-3 text-green-900 translate-y-px bg-green-100 rounded-full sm:-ml-16">
                {{ section.icon | svgContents('w-5 h-5 sm:w-6 sm:h-6') | safe }}
                </span>
                {%- endif -%}
                {{ section.title | safe }}
              </h2>

              <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 mt-2 mb-4 text-base text-blue-500 hover:underline hover:text-blue-600">
                <span># Kopier lenke</span>
                {# {{ '/src/_includes/svg/icons/link.svg' | svgContents('w-3.5 h-3.5') | safe }} #}
              </a>

              <div class="grid gap-4">
              {%- for block in section.contentBlocks -%}

                {%- if block.type === 'markdown' -%}
                  <div class="markdown">
                    {{ block.data  | markdown | safe }}
                  </div>
                {%- endif -%}

                {%- if block.type === 'actions' -%}
                <div class="grid gap-1.5 sm:flex">
                  {%- for item in block.data -%}
                    {{ button(
                      {
                        text: item.text,
                        href: '#',
                        variant: item.variant
                      }
                    ) }}
                  {%- endfor -%}
                </div>
                {%- endif -%}

                {%- if block.type === 'microcards' -%}
                  <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold">{{ block.title | safe }}</h4>
                  <div class="flex mt-1 flex-wrap gap-1.5">
                    {%- for item in block.data -%}
                      {{ microcard({
                        text: item.text,
                        dot: item.dot
                      }) }}
                    {%- endfor -%}
                  </div>
                {%- endif -%}

                {%- if block.type === 'tiles' -%}
                  <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold">{{ block.title | safe }}</h4>
                  <div class="grid mt-1 border-b border-gray-300">
                    {%- for item in block.data -%}
                      <div class="relative flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-3 fine:hover:z-10 {{ item.theme }} border-t border-gray-300">
                        {{ item.icon | svgContents('max-w-16 h-auto w-[calc(8vw+1rem)]') | safe }}
                        <a class="flex-1 text-xl font-semibold leading-snug after:absolute after:inset-0" href="#">{{ item.title }}</a>
                      </div>
                    {%- endfor -%}
                  </div>
                {%- endif -%}

                {%- if block.type === 'line' -%}
                  <hr class="border-deepblue-100" />
                {%- endif -%}

              {%- endfor -%}
              </div>
            </div>
            {%- endif -%}
          {%- endfor -%}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
{%- endblock -%}
